### PR types
Bug fixes

### PR changes
Others. Helper function for convering the format of label-studio to doccano.

### Description

Fix json file reading error.
- Only json line format was accpted, which is not the default export option in labelstudio, making error for directly output json or formatted json file. The reading procedure was fixed to adapt both the json line format and detended format.

title: [LLM] Support tensor parallelism  for save and load
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleNLP/pull/26 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features
### PR changes
<!-- One of [ Models | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
Others
### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Support tensor parallelism  for save and load

为save_pretrained新增了`merge_tensor_parallel`参数。
- 当`merge_tensor_parallel=True`, 其他分片的参数
- 会通过网络通信，将参数传递到`tensor_parallel_rank=0`的节点存储。权重名称`model_state.pdparams`
-  当`merge_tensor_parallel=False`,  各分片独立存储，权重名称`model_state.tp00.pdparams model_state.tp01.pdparams ...`
- 注意，当 tensor parallelism 和sharding、data parallelism共同使用是，只需要对 `sharding_parallel_rank=0, data_parallell_rank=0`的节点保存一份参数即可。如此处判断：https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleNLP/blob/0c0d5eb8adcde08e4d13d39ba028267414049472/paddlenlp/trainer/training_args.py#L850-L852

```python
model.save_pretrained(save_dir=tempdir, merge_tensor_parallel=True)
```
完整测试代码如下：
```python
import os
import tempfile

import paddle

from paddlenlp.transformers import GLMModel


def func(self, *args, **kwargs):
    return


# 屏蔽init_weights
GLMModel.init_weights = func


def main():
    tensor_parallel_degree = paddle.distributed.get_world_size()
    tensor_parallel_rank = paddle.distributed.get_rank()
    strategy = paddle.distributed.fleet.DistributedStrategy()
    strategy.hybrid_configs = {
        "dp_degree": 1,
        "mp_degree": tensor_parallel_degree,
        "pp_degree": 1,
        "sharding_degree": 1,
    }
    paddle.distributed.fleet.init(is_collective=True, strategy=strategy)

    model = GLMModel.from_pretrained(
        "THUDM/glm-large-chinese",
        tensor_parallel_degree=tensor_parallel_degree,
        tensor_parallel_rank=tensor_parallel_rank,
        dtype="float16",
        low_cpu_mem_usage=True,
    )

    model.eval()
    ret = model(input_ids=paddle.arange(100, 110, dtype="int64").reshape([1, -1]))
    print("paddle tensor parallel results", ret.logits.abs().mean().item())

    with tempfile.TemporaryDirectory() as tempdir:
        # save 为切分好的分片 merge_tensor_parallel=False (默认方式)
        model.save_pretrained(save_dir=tempdir, merge_tensor_parallel=False)
        paddle.distributed.barrier()
        print(os.listdir(tempdir))
        load_model = GLMModel.from_pretrained(
            tempdir,
            tensor_parallel_degree=tensor_parallel_degree,
            tensor_parallel_rank=tensor_parallel_rank,
            dtype="float16",
            low_cpu_mem_usage=True,
        )
        load_model.eval()
        ret = load_model(input_ids=paddle.arange(100, 110, dtype="int64").reshape([1, -1]))
        print("paddle tensor parallel results", ret.logits.abs().mean().item())

    with tempfile.TemporaryDirectory() as tempdir:
        object_list = []
        paddle.distributed.all_gather_object(object_list, tempdir)
        tempdir = object_list[0]
        # save 为完整参数 merge_tensor_parallel=True
        model.save_pretrained(save_dir=tempdir, merge_tensor_parallel=True)
        paddle.distributed.barrier()
        print(os.listdir(tempdir))
        load_model = GLMModel.from_pretrained(
            tempdir,
            tensor_parallel_degree=tensor_parallel_degree,
            tensor_parallel_rank=tensor_parallel_rank,
            dtype="float16",
            low_cpu_mem_usage=True,
        )
        load_model.eval()
        ret = load_model(input_ids=paddle.arange(100, 110, dtype="int64").reshape([1, -1]))

        print("paddle tensor parallel results", ret.logits.abs().mean().item())


if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()

```
